<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="proxy-page" data-turbo="false">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Poplink</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "links" %>
  <style>
    /* Critical CSS to prevent layout shift */
    html.proxy-page, body.proxy-page {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .proxy-page #content-frame {
      width: 100%;
      height: calc(100% - 80px);
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }
    .proxy-page #cta-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 80px;
      z-index: 9999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="proxy-page">
  <iframe id="content-frame" src="<%= @link.original_url %>"></iframe>

  <div id="iframe-error">
    <h2>⚠️ 이 콘텐츠는 프레임에서 표시할 수 없습니다</h2>
    <p>대상 웹사이트의 보안 설정으로 인해 여기에 표시할 수 없습니다.</p>
    <p><a href="<%= @link.original_url %>" target="_blank">여기를 클릭하여 원본 페이지를 방문하세요</a></p>
  </div>

  <div id="cta-overlay" style="<%= cta_overlay_style(@link) %>">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <% if @link.cta_text.present? %>
        <span class="cta-text"><%= @link.cta_text %></span>
      <% end %>
      <% if @link.cta_link.present? %>
        <a href="<%= @link.cta_link %>" class="cta-button" target="_blank">
          <%= @link.cta_button_text || '자세히 보기' %>
        </a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Detect if iframe fails to load (X-Frame-Options blocking)
    const iframe = document.getElementById('content-frame');
    const errorDiv = document.getElementById('iframe-error');

    iframe.addEventListener('error', function() {
      iframe.style.display = 'none';
      errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
    });

    // Timeout fallback (some browsers don't fire error event)
    setTimeout(function() {
      try {
        const iframeDoc = iframe.contentDocument || iframe.contentWindow.document;
        if (!iframeDoc) {
          iframe.style.display = 'none';
          errorDiv.style.display = 'block';
        }
      } catch (e) {
        // Cross-origin access denied - this is actually normal
        // Only show error if iframe is completely empty
      }
    }, 3000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
